snippet.title: Combat Mission Battle for Normandy || in 2 minutes
snippet.description:
Combat Mission Battle for Normandy faithfully recreates the experience of tactical land warfare in Western France during World War Two. The Base Game covers the three month period following the Allied D-Day landings, from Operation Overlord in June through the Cobra Breakout in August.

🎮 Buy now on Steam ➡️ https://bit.ly/3QRhAa8
💬 Join the Discord Server ➡️ https://bit.ly/3SABlEi
🧿 More info on Matrix➡️ https://bit.ly/3FYvnFr
